		<description>An armored juggernaut equipped with advanced sonic resonance technology, the sonic tank emits powerful shockwaves that destabilize structures and rupture enemies' bodies, rendering adversaries helpless in its wake.\n\nA bit more resilient than a Bulldog. Needs more expensive ammo, requiring uranium energy cells.\n\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Crew:&lt;/color&gt; Driver x1, Gunner x1\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Fuel type:&lt;/color&gt; Chemfuel\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Ammo type:&lt;/color&gt; Uranium energy cells.\n\nInspired on the Atreides Sonic Tank from Dune II, Battle for Arrakis, famous for being the first ever RTS game.</description>
